data.text:
“A new chapter has started: qbilon GmbH becomes part of Paessler AG”

qbilon GmbH’s decision to join the Paessler Group combines Qbilon’s core competence – providing complete transparency for IT landscapes – with the best possible monitoring experience through Paessler.

We look forward to working with Paessler and will continue to pursue our goal of providing our customers with comprehensive knowledge of their IT landscapes so they can operate with optimal efficiency, reliability and security.

With Paessler at our side, we are confident to accelerate the realization of the vision we set out four years ago when we founded the company.
